Package: pdftools
Type: Package
Title: Text Extraction and Rendering of PDF Documents
Version: 1.0
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: Utilities based on libpoppler for extracting text,
    fonts, attachments and metadata from a pdf file. Also implements
    rendering of PDF to bitmaps on supported platforms.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://ropensci.org/blog/2016/03/01/pdftools-and-jeroen
    https://github.com/ropensci/pdftools
BugReports: https://github.com/ropensci/pdftools/issues
SystemRequirements: Poppler C++ interface library and headers
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: jpeg, png, webp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
